  "english": [
    "<b>to them: I observe that they sweat,</b> i.e., they exude liquid from their exterior. <b>And since they sweat, they certainly absorb, and are</b> therefore <b>prohibited.</b> The Gemara asks: <b>What is the reason</b> that they cannot be rendered permitted by purging with hot water? It is because <b>the Torah attested with regard to an earthenware vessel that</b> substances absorbed in it are <b>never expelled from its walls.</b>",
    "The Gemara reiterates its question: Mareimar ruled that glazed earthenware absorbs leavened bread permanently, but he did not rule likewise with regard to wine. But in <b>what</b> way <b>is</b> leavened bread <b>different from wine</b> used for an idolatrous <b>libation?</b> Why is it <b>that Mareimar taught</b> with regard to <b>them: All glazed earthenware vessels are permitted,</b> even if they have contained wine of gentiles?",
    "The Gemara adds: <b>And if you would say</b> that these cases are different, as <b>leavened bread</b> is prohibited <b>by Torah law</b> whereas <b>wine</b> used for <b>a libation</b> is prohibited <b>by rabbinic</b> law, that is difficult: <b>But</b> there is a principle that <b>all</b> ordinances <b>that the Sages instituted, they instituted them parallel to Torah law.</b> Although this wine is prohibited by rabbinic law, it is subject to the same <i>halakhot</i> as leavened bread. The Gemara answers: <b>This one’s use is with hot</b> substances, <b>and that one’s use is with cold</b> substances. Wine is drunk while it is cold and is therefore absorbed to a lesser extent than leavened bread, which is often cooked in the vessel.",
    "The Gemara relates: <b>Rabbi Akiva happened to</b> come to the city of <b>Ginzak,</b> whose residents <b>asked him</b> three questions to which he did not know the answer: First, <b>does one fast for hours, or does one not fast for hours?</b> The answer to the question <b>was not available to</b> Rabbi Akiva. Second, are clay <b>jars</b> that <b>belong to gentiles</b> permanently <b>prohibited, or</b> can they be rendered <b>permitted?</b> The answer <b>was not available to him.</b> Third, <b>in what</b> garments <b>did Moses serve all seven days of</b> the Tabernacle’s <b>inauguration,</b> as acting priest when Aaron and his sons were initiated into the priesthood? Moses presumably did not wear the priestly vestments, as he himself was not a priest. Once again, the answer <b>was not available to him.</b>",
    "Rabbi Akiva <b>came</b> and <b>asked</b> these questions in the <b>study hall. They said to him:</b> The <b><i>halakha</i></b> is that <b>one fasts for hours, and if he completed</b> the fast <b>he prays the prayer of a fast. And</b> the <b><i>halakha</i></b> is that the <b>jars</b> that <b>belong to gentiles are permitted after</b> they have not been used for <b>twelve months.</b> Finally, <b>in what</b> garments <b>did Moses serve</b> during <b>the seven days of inauguration?</b> He did not serve in his own clothes, nor in the regular priestly vestments, but <b>in</b> a special <b>white cloak. Rav Kahana teaches:</b> Moses served <b>in a white cloak without a hem.</b>",
    "§ The mishna teaches that residual grape <b>seeds and grape skins</b> that <b>belong to gentiles</b> are prohibited. <b>The Sages taught:</b> Moist grape <b>seeds and grape skins</b> that <b>belong to gentiles</b> are <b>prohibited,</b> but <b>dry ones are permitted.</b> The Gemara asks: <b>Which are</b> considered <b>moist and which are</b> considered <b>dry? Rav Yehuda says</b> that <b>Shmuel says:</b> Grape residues are considered <b>moist</b> for <b>all</b> of the first <b>twelve months</b> after the grapes were pressed, and <b>dry after</b> the first <b>twelve months.</b>",
    "<b>It was stated</b> that <b>Rabba bar bar Ḥana says</b> that <b>Rabbi Yoḥanan says: When</b> these grape residues <b>are prohibited,</b> one is <b>prohibited even from</b> deriving <b>benefit</b> from them. <b>When they are permitted, they are permitted even with regard to consumption.</b>",
    "<b>Rav Zevid says:</b> With regard to <b>these yeasts</b> produced from <b>the wine of Arameans, after twelve months</b> of <b>the year they are permitted. Rav Ḥaviva, son of Rava, says:</b> With regard to <b>these jugs</b> that belong to gentiles, <b>after twelve months</b> of <b>the year they are permitted. Rav Ḥaviva says:</b> With regard to <b>these</b>"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לְהוּ: אֲנָא חָזֵינָא לְהוּ דְּמִדַּיְּיתִי, וְכֵיוָן דְּמִדַּיְּיתִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וַדַּאי בָּלְעִי וַאֲסִירִי. מַאי טַעְמָא? הַתּוֹרָה הֵעִידָה עַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּלִי חֶרֶס שֶׁאֵינוֹ יוֹצֵא מִידֵי דּוֹפְנוֹ לְעוֹלָם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מַאי",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁנָא מִיַּיִן נֶסֶךְ, דְּדָרֵשׁ לְהוּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Mareimar, sixth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2198\" data-full-name=\"Mareimar\" data-name-he=\"מרימר\">מָרִימָר</span>: כּוּלְּהוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מָאנֵי דְקוּנְיָא שְׁרֵי? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְכִי תֵּימָא: חָמֵץ דְּאוֹרָיְיתָא, יֵין",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נֶסֶךְ דְּרַבָּנַן — וְהָא כֹּל דְּתַקּוּן רַבָּנַן כְּעֵין",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאוֹרָיְיתָא תַּקּוּן! זֶה תַּשְׁמִישׁוֹ בְּחַמִּין, וְזֶה",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תַּשְׁמִישׁוֹ בְּצוֹנֵן. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Akiva I, fourth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2465\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Akiva I\" data-name-he=\"רבי עקיבא בן יוסף\">רַבִּי עֲקִיבָא</span> אִיקְּלַע לְגִינְזַק, בְּעוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִינֵּיהּ: מִתְעַנִּין לְשָׁעוֹת אוֹ אֵין מִתְעַנִּין לְשָׁעוֹת?",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָא הֲוָה בִּידֵיהּ. קַנְקַנִּים שֶׁל גּוֹיִם",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲסוּרִין אוֹ מוּתָּרִין? לָא הֲוָה בִּידֵיהּ. בַּמֶּה",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שִׁימֵּשׁ מֹשֶׁה כׇּל שִׁבְעַת יְמֵי הַמִּלּוּאִים? לָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הֲוָה בִּידֵיהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-131\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\">אֲתָא שְׁאֵל בֵּי מִדְרְשָׁא, אָמְרִי:</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-131\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\">הִלְכְתָא מִתְעַנִּין לְשָׁעוֹת, וְאִם הִשְׁלִים — מִתְפַּלֵּל</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-131\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\">תְּפִלַּת תַּעֲנִית. וְהִלְכְתָא קַנְקַנִּים שֶׁל גּוֹיִם לְאַחַר</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-131\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\">שְׁנֵים עָשָׂר חֹדֶשׁ מוּתָּרִין. בַּמֶּה שִׁימֵּשׁ</a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-131\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\">מֹשֶׁה שִׁבְעַת יְמֵי הַמִּלּוּאִים? בְּחָלוּק לָבָן. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Kahana, the brother of II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2004\" data-full-name=\"Rav Kahana, the brother of II\" data-name-he=\"רב כהנא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-2098\">רַב</span></a>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-131\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\"><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Kahana, the brother of II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2004\" data-full-name=\"Rav Kahana, the brother of II\" data-name-he=\"רב כהנא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-2098\">כָּהֲנָא</span> מַתְנֵי: בְּחָלוּק לָבָן שֶׁאֵין בּוֹ אִימְּרָא</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"131\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"105\" data-sentence-id=\"5\">§</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><a class=\"piska-quote-link\" data-piska-quote-group=\"piska-quote-132\" href=\"/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-19\" title=\"Mishnah source: Avodah Zarah 34a\">הַחַרְצַנִּים וְהַזַּגִּים שֶׁל גּוֹיִם וְכוּ׳</a><span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"132\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> תָּנוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "רַבָּנַן: הַחַרְצַנִּים וְהַזַּגִּים שֶׁל גּוֹיִם, לַחִין — אֲסוּרִין, יְבֵשִׁים — מוּתָּרִים. הֵי נִינְהוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "לַחִין וְהֵי נִינְהוּ יְבֵשִׁין? אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Yehuda bar Yeḥezkel\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">רַב יְהוּדָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Shmuel II, first-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2763\" data-full-name=\"Shmuel II\" data-name-he=\"שמואל\">שְׁמוּאֵל</span>: לַחִין — כׇּל שְׁנֵים עָשָׂר חֹדֶשׁ, יְבֵשִׁים —",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "לְאַחַר שְׁנֵים עָשָׂר חֹדֶשׁ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אִתְּמַר, אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba bar bar Ḥanna, third-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2594\" data-full-name=\"Rabba bar bar Ḥanna\" data-name-he=\"רבה בר בר חנה\">רַבָּה בַּר בַּר חָנָה</span> אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II, second-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1570\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yoḥanan II\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוחנן\">רַבִּי יוֹחָנָן</span>: כְּשֶׁהֵן אֲסוּרִין —",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "אֲסוּרִין אֲפִילּוּ בַּהֲנָאָה, כְּשֶׁהֵן מוּתָּרִין — מוּתָּרִין אֲפִילּוּ בַּאֲכִילָה. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"993\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman\" data-name-he=\"רב זביד\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-2103\">רַב</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Naḥman, fifth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"993\" data-full-name=\"Rav Naḥman\" data-name-he=\"רב זביד\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-2103\">זְבִיד</span>: הַאי דּוּרְדְּיָּא דְּחַמְרָא דַּאֲרַמָּאֵי, בָּתַר תְּרֵיסַר יַרְחֵי שַׁתָּא שָׁרֵי. אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Aḥa, son of Rav, sixth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"297\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa, son of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב אחא בריה דרבא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-2104\">רַב</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "0px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Aḥa, son of Rav, sixth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"297\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa, son of Rav\" data-name-he=\"רב אחא בריה דרבא\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-2104\">חֲבִיבָא בְּרֵיהּ דְּרָבָא</span>: הָנֵי גּוּלְפֵי, בָּתַר תְּרֵיסַר יַרְחֵי שַׁתָּא שָׁרֵי. אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ḥaviva from Sura, seventh-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1051\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ḥaviva from Sura\" data-name-he=\"רב חביבא מסורא דפרת\">רַב חֲבִיבָא</span>: הָנֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>דְּמִדַּיְּיתִי</b> מזיעין דופניהם מבחוץ",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מחמת בליעותן: <b>הַתּוֹרָה הֵעִידָה.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דכתיב ישבר דאין לו טהרה אלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שבירה: <b>זֶה תַּשְׁמִישׁוֹ בְּחַמִּין.</b> לענין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חמץ נשתמשו כל ימות השנה חמין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ובלעי טפי: <b>לְשָׁעוֹת.</b> כגון שקיבל עליו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תענית משש שעות ולמעלה ומיהו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא טעם כלום מתחלה כל היום אבל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא לשם תענית נתכוין בראשונה:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:4:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לְאַחַר שְׁנֵים עָשָׂר חֹדֶשׁ מוּתָּרִין.</b> מיד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בלי תיקון ואם רצה להשתמש קודם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לכן ממלאן במים כדאמרן: <b>מֹשֶׁה.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא נשתמש בבגדי כהונה דכתיב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ועשית בגדי קדש לאהרן אחיך והוא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היה זר אצלן ועל פי הדבור שימש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא הוזכרו בגדים: <b>אִימְּרָא.</b> שפה.",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יש אומר שלא יחשדוהו ששם בה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מתרומת המשכן ולאו מילתא שהרי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כבר נגמרה המלאכה ובשעת עבודה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:5:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מהיכן שקיל: <b>דּוּרְדְּיָּא.</b> שמרים:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Avodah Zarah 34a:8:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    }
  ],
  "vilna_piskaot": [
    {
      "id": 131,
      "symbol": "׃",
      "raw_symbol": "׃",
      "line_number": 18,
      "mishnah_ref": "Avodah Zarah 34a",
      "mishnah_href": "/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-13",
      "mishnah_line_number": 13,
      "quote_text": "אֲתָא שְׁאֵל בֵּי מִדְרְשָׁא, אָמְרִי: הִלְכְתָא מִתְעַנִּין לְשָׁעוֹת, וְאִם הִשְׁלִים — מִתְפַּלֵּל תְּפִלַּת תַּעֲנִית. וְהִלְכְתָא קַנְקַנִּים שֶׁל גּוֹיִם לְאַחַר שְׁנֵים עָשָׂר חֹדֶשׁ מוּתָּרִין. בַּמֶּה שִׁימֵּשׁ מֹשֶׁה שִׁבְעַת יְמֵי הַמִּלּוּאִים? בְּחָלוּק לָבָן. רַב כָּהֲנָא מַתְנֵי: בְּחָלוּק לָבָן שֶׁאֵין בּוֹ אִימְּרָא"
    },
    {
      "id": 132,
      "symbol": "׃",
      "raw_symbol": "׃",
      "line_number": 19,
      "mishnah_ref": "Avodah Zarah 34a",
      "mishnah_href": "/avodah_zarah/34a#gemara-line-19",
      "mishnah_line_number": 19,
      "quote_text": "הַחַרְצַנִּים וְהַזַּגִּים שֶׁל גּוֹיִם וְכוּ׳"
    }
  ],
  "steinsaltz_sugyot": [],
  "tosafot": [
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<big><b>שֶׁאֵינוֹ יוֹצֵא מִידֵי דּוֹפְנוֹ לְעוֹלָם.</b></big> וליכא למימר דהיא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "870px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "גופה נילף בק\"ו דאיכא למימר שבועת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביטוי יוכיח ומיהו במה מצינו מצי גמר לה ונראה דהיינו הא דפריך לקמן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליגמר נמי שבועת פקדון משבועת העדות למושבע מפי אחרים וכ\"ת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אדרבה נילף מביטוי מסתברא דאיכא למילף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טפי מעדות שכן חטא תבעיה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כפריה ועבריה <big><b>ה\"ג</b></big>. ואית",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דל\"ג ועבריה משום",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דשבועת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ביטוי איתא [נמי]",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לשעבר לר\"ע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ול\"נ דא\"כ תבעיה וכפריה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תרי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "180px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מילי נינהו מדקאמר הנך נפישן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולקמן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בשמעתין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מוכח",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דחדא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "היא דפריך",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אדרבה מעדות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ה\"ל למילף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שכן חטא הדיוט",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בשבועה תבעיה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וכפריה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואואין ומשני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הנך נפישן ואי חשיבי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בתרי אם כן לא נפישן <big><b>דאי אית ליה.</b></big> משמע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הכא דר' אחא אית ליה אומדנא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בדיני נפשות ותימה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דבפ' אחד דיני ממונות (<a href=\"/sanhedrin/37a\">סנהדרין דף לז.</a>) גבי כיצד מאיימין על דיני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נפשות שמא תאמרו מאומד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ראיתם ודייק בגמ' (<a href=\"/avodah_zarah/340b\">שם:</a>) הא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בדיני ממונות אמרינן כמאן כר' אחא כו' משמע דלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "איירי רבי אחא בדיני נפשות וי\"ל דודאי מעיקרא דס\"ד דלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מיתוקם כרבנן ע\"כ מוקי לה כר' אחא ואית לן למימר דלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "איירי אלא בדיני",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ממונות דוקא ולא בדיני נפשות כי היכי דתיתוקם מתני' כוותיה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל לפי המסקנא דמוקי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לה כרבנן מ\"ל דר' אחא אית ליה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אומדנא אפי' בדיני נפשות אבל עוד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תימה דמשמע משום דאית ליה בדיני ממונות אית ליה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמי בדיני נפשות וא\"כ אפי' לית ליה דר' אחא משכחת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לה אומדנא בדיני נפשות לכ\"ע כמו שעלתה לו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נשיכה על ראשו ונקב קרום של מוח דאפי'",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רבנן מודו בהאי אומדנא כדמוכח בפרק כל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הנשבעין לקמן (<a href=\"/avodah_zarah/46b\">דף מו:</a>) כגון שעלתה לו נשיכה על גבו ובין אצילי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ידיו וי\"ל דהמ\"ל ולטעמיך <big><b>על פי</b></big>. חבר היה וכמ\"ד (<a href=\"/sanhedrin/8b\">מכות דף ו: ובסנהדרין ח:</a>) דאין",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צריך התראה ואע\"פ שהיה כאן פירכוס ובלבול רוח שהרי בחורבה היה לא היה פוטרו בשביל כך",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דדוקא גבי גלות הוא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דפטרי' ליה בפ' בתרא דיבמות (דף קכ: ושם) משום דמייתרי קראי דכתיב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כמה זמנין ויפל עליו וימות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "850px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל ממיתת ב\"ד לא מיפטר בהכי תדע דהא אמרינן (<a href=\"/sanhedrin/78b\">סנהדרין עח:</a>) שהיו חובשים",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אותו ומיהו מכאן יש לדחות ולאוקמיה כגון",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמחייה בביתא דשישא ולא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרכיס וכן צריך לאוקומה למאן דמוקי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "860px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בפ' אלו נערות (<a href=\"/ketubot/33b\">כתובות לג:</a>) לקרא בשוגג ומאי ונקה ונקה מגלות <big><b>אי טריפה הרג</b></big>. תימה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הא אזלינן בתר רובא דמרוצח",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דייקינן לה בפ\"ק דחולין (דף יא: ושם)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלא חיישינן דלמא במקום סייף נקב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוה וי\"ל דמיירי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כגון דאיכא קמן חד טריפה וחד",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שלם",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דצריך לידע",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "930px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "",
      "text": "איזה מהם הרג",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Avodah Zarah 34a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    }
  ]
}